{"tid":1957776,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港學術自由倒退 如埃塞俄比亞","createTime":"2020-04-04T06:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T10:58:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"85deb9f50ea89e11554e29d829c88e9efc146f8a","tid":1957776,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T06:58:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200404/FPIXAWM7WBAVVWU663W3PBWJUU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200404%2FFPIXAWM7WBAVVWU663W3PBWJUU%2F&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQygEOIADdcgve6BSnlMLQ7pQ%3D&h=1e070fb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200404%2FFPIXAWM7WBAVVWU663W3PBWJUU%2F&h=b636242d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200404/FPIXAWM7WBAVVWU663W3PBWJUU/</a><br />\n<br />\n港學術自由倒退 如埃塞俄比亞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200404/large/1585930567_79db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200404%2Flarge%2F1585930567_79db.jpg&h=e6ca8311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港大畢業生評議會去年發動投票，促請特首林鄭月娥辭任港大校監。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港在反送中運動受政權打壓，人權自由面對前所未有挑戰。有調查顯示，香港的學術自由被評為C級，學術自由指數只有0.442分，與0.440分的埃塞俄比亞相若。<br />\n<br />\n特首校監制損院校自主<br />\n<br />\n全球公共政策研究所（Global Public Policy Institute）公佈最新全球學術自由指數，調查以五個指標作為計算單位，包括研究及教學自由、學術交流自由、院校自主、校園完善度，以及學術和文化表達的自由。結果顯示香港自2000年起，五方面分數皆不斷下跌。<br />\n<br />\n各指標以4分為滿分，學術交流自由從當年的3.5分跌至現時低於3分；研究及教學的自由、學術和文化表達的自由兩項，現時均低於2.5分；校園完善度更跌破2分。香港各公營專上院校均奉行特首校監必然制，院校自主一欄更僅約1.3分。<br />\n<br />\n香港學術自由被評為C級，學術自由指數只有0.442分，成為過去五年學術自由倒退最嚴重的地方之一，其餘地方包括印度、土耳其、烏克蘭、巴西、巴基斯坦、利比亞、也門等。得分最高的葡萄牙及烏拉圭為0.971，被評為A級；中國的學術自由指數則屬E級，評分為0.101。<br />\n<br />\n■記者盧珮瑤"},{"pid":"b12d3a71b9e8fa8534e273f9a4772521b5444eac","tid":1957776,"uid":8014,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:00:29.000Z","msg":"林鄭又贏 又考第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e624a5cff2801920af6322f0922732dcb5a7e551","tid":1957776,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T07:01:53.000Z","msg":"0.101<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a10afa0dd9ce6be9f1f2e916029ae69fe004099","tid":1957776,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T06:18:58.000Z","msg":"談得失：同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1262ba183404a5ea0bb652f79c7b369303518224","tid":1957776,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"港共"},{"pid":"be2176f9846d0d3fc1fe21bc5eb41988994d9977","tid":1957776,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6431e194d17ab1a85bb35a72713128cd4566c446","tid":1957776,"uid":312526,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T07:08:53.000Z","msg":"又話自由多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今舖點拆"},{"pid":"582f448270105433502f80eb0ea016fec44f38d4","tid":1957776,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"後知後覺 當年雞珍指定要傳位俾譚狗 我就知香港終於追得上埃塞俄比亞嘅「發展」步伐喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec64cc35d03334171ae2f3bfb792877d1c66892e","tid":1957776,"uid":335434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6431e194d17ab1a85bb35a72713128cd4566c446","tid":1957776,"uid":312526,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T07:0